data.description: Escape to your own private oasis with this charming lakefront retreat nestled in a peaceful lakeside community. Whether you're seeking a serene year-round residence or an inviting Airbnb or Weekend getaway, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort and relaxation. The inviting interior features an open layout with vaulted beam ceilings w and abundant natural light. Breakfast bar area has Quartz countertops. A cozy loft area provides additional living space or a peaceful retreat. Enjoy convenient access to the water with your own private covered single slip dock with boat lift  perfect for boat storage or lounging by the lake. Situated on a level lot for easy access and outdoor enjoyment. Host gatherings or have morning coffee on the spacious deck overlooking the lake. Bathrooms have been remodeled home has new flooring, new paint, light fixtures, fans and outdoor lighting. Boat included in the sale of property.
